name: Breakpoint-sharer
body: ### breakpoint sharer Breakpoint Sharer is just a simple Chrome Extension that enables you to import/export debugging breakpoints, to explain/learn code logic better ### Chrome Extension install here : https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/hkbgnljbklddbfmkmeaoolmdflbbofmi/publish-accepted ### usage Basically it is similar to original Chrome DevTool, with breakpoint import/export function, but lacking many many many other features.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
